4.000Z","msg":"兩人「不斷打電話」滋擾被起底警員判囚14天緩刑兩年　官斥被告行為不要得<br />\n<br />\n一名警員於今年6月4日在街上清理路障，事後被網民在社交媒體上「起底」，收到逾200個滋擾電話。警方憑電訊公司紀錄追查，拘捕涉案兩名男子。兩人今（4日）於西九龍裁判法院提堂，各被控一項「不斷打電話」罪，認罪後被判囚14天、緩刑24個月。裁判官王詩麗批評被告行為不要得，對執勤的警員構成滋擾。"},{"pid":"030283b8badd2348af6205c66dcfa6c033ed02bc","tid":2320652,"uid":244617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"做咩用自己電話打<br />\n落街用電話亭打 打一萬次都搵你唔到啦"},{"pid":"68dc7c673086bc5eb53a426e6f340b5f584b0f09","tid":2320652,"uid":169048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"七次=不斷打電話罪<br />\n<br />\n告我老細ok？"},{"pid":"f6adade22e77738e2b6a65e1cd3a0d810bcaefc8","tid":2320652,"uid":360274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6ef5de4cdf9f2d86eb062138204e8f4fefbe707","tid":2320652,"uid":186431,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"想人獸交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"睇內文啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"729a00c4605cd970ae264bbd8157513fe3f026ad","tid":2320652,"uid":36248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ab6d5b45cac97226a0992e4569c6510f69b68d8","tid":2320652,"uid":117908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"咁似193<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"第一眼都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1d910acb25fa62c8da6b18aed68ae064a9915a","tid":2320652,"uid":121125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:04:21.000Z","msg":"幾型 無罪釋放啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1592571bf1ae1b922b457a24b2251553b2a223","tid":2320652,"uid":382841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:09:14.000Z","msg":"佢都係為左出氣<br />\nBTW,好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkg